{
  "stem": "7069.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't talk about fruit or vegetable, the reason for it being that it wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nobody got it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So the children-- what I described from the black water until the end, that's what the children received.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sundays, we got a piece of margarine and a little bag of sugar sometimes, little, tiny-- like a a restaurant size and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But now, as you-- talking about the children-- as you can imagine, it was nothing to keep small children alive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In fact, many, many, many women were delivered to the camp pregnant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In other words, the fact that on-- that when the Nazis had the order to clear out Seventh Street east from this block to that block, they would pick up everybody that was there, whether the people were-- could walk, whether they would have to carry it on a-- carry out on stretchers, old folks, young folks, babies, women that were pregnant.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Didn't make any difference.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They all went onto that truck and were sent to the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was in a separate part.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But every once in a while, we were able to see her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother and I, fortunately, were able to stay together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, well, first of all, when we arrived in the camp, we looked around us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we noticed that most people have, and all over their exposed skin, blotches.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them had severe sores from scratches, open that were dried and, and, and very severe-looking sores, scratches.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were wondering, at first, what that was all about, what that came from.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lot of people had it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It looked like almost everyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, it didn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We found out what that-- how that was coming about.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
